node.text: Following on from my support of @mindcharity through the @leytonorientfc partnership I’m proud to be supporting #MentalHealthMinute with @heads_together and @radiocentre_uk. Whoever you are, and whatever you’re going through, it’s important that you remember you’re not alone. #MentalHealthAwarenessWeek

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Harry Kane on September 16, 2021 tagging @lucasmoura7, and @spursofficial. May be an image of 2 people.

node.text: Very proud to have made the most European appearances in @spursofficial club history. Tough game and loads to improve on for the weekend.

node.text: Good three games with @england, now ready for the @premierleague. @soccersupplement got me covered. #UpYourGame

node.text: Gutted not to see out the win tonight. Loads of positives from these three games and a huge step closer to World Cup qualification. 🦁🦁🦁
